OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FMansfield District Council needs to
OL,7,Fspend up to #600,000 on further
OL,8,Fstabilising works at an old quarry
OL,9,Fwhere a landslide happened six years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FIn November 7, 2019, the cliff face at
OL,13,FBerry Hill collapsed, sending 1,300
OL,14,Ftonnes of debris and mud cascading
OL,15,Ftowards residential properties on two
OL,16,Fcul-de-sacs.
OL,18,FIt led to 60 residents being evacuated
OL,19,Ffrom their homes.
