OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FUrgent repair work was completed
OL,7,Fwithin weeks so people could move back
OL,8,Fin, and after two more landslides in
OL,9,Fthe next two years, permanent
OL,10,Fstabilisation works took place,
OL,11,Fstarting in the spring of 2021 and
OL,12,Ffinishing in autumn of 2022.
OL,14,FBut now, four and a half years on,
OL,15,Fgeology experts Fairhurst have told
OL,16,Fthe council that more remedial work
OL,17,Fneeds to be completed in a "timely
OL,18,Fmanner" to mitigate further risk.
