OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FAt a meeting on Thursday, December 4,
OL,7,Fcouncil chief executive James
OL,8,FBiddlestone awarded the works contract
OL,9,F` the value of which has not been
OL,10,Fdisclosed ` to an anonymous
OL,11,Fcontractor, which was one of two
OL,12,Fcompanies that bid for the chance to
OL,13,Fcomplete the work.
OL,15,FDocuments say the anticipated maximum
OL,16,Fcost of the contract is #600,000.
