OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FBerry Hill Quarry, on the south side
OL,7,Fof Mansfield city centre, was a
OL,8,Fsandstone quarry used for the
OL,9,Fextraction of sandstone in the second
OL,10,Fhalf of the 20th century.
OL,12,FAfter it closed, a new housing estate
OL,13,Fwas built in its wake. This was
OL,14,Fcompleted in 2011.
OL,16,FThe streets are looked down on by the
OL,17,Fcliff faces of the quarry, which back
OL,18,Fdirectly onto the back gardens of some
OL,19,Fof the new homes, on Bank End Close
OL,20,Fand Stone Bank.
