OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FIn the week commencing November 4,
OL,7,F2019, extremely heavy rain led to the
OL,8,Fslope collapsing, sending debris,
OL,9,Fincluding dislodged trees, into the
OL,10,Fgardens of properties across Bank End
OL,11,FClose.
OL,13,FNo one was injured at the time.
OL,15,FImmediately, 32 homes were evacuated,
OL,16,Fwith 19 remaining empty for two weeks.
