OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FMansfield District Council put
OL,7,Fresidents in temporary accommodation
OL,8,Fwhile they undertook emergency works
OL,9,Fto clear the material and put
OL,10,Ftemporary protection in place.
OL,12,FCompensation was later provided to
OL,13,Fresidents, and Fairhurst was
OL,14,Fcontracted to complete regular surveys
OL,15,Fof the cliff face, which continued for
OL,16,Ftwo years.
