OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FAfter meetings and an independent
OL,7,Finvestigation by a solicitor was
OL,8,Fpublished in July 2020, the council,
OL,9,Fwhich owns the land, said it was
OL,10,Fsatisfied that the new estate had been
OL,11,Fbuilt sensibly and according to
OL,12,Fplanning conditions.
OL,14,FBut the solicitor also said that
OL,15,Fideally, no development should have
OL,16,Fbeen permitted on the site until "the
OL,17,Fstabilisation of the quarry face in
OL,18,Fboth the long and short term had been
OL,19,Fsecured."
