OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FHe added: "It is highly questionable
OL,7,Fas to whether the Council should have
OL,8,Fadopted the cliff top.
OL,10,F"In the event that it did wish to
OL,11,Fproceed with the adoption of the cliff
OL,12,Ftop it should have taken all
OL,13,Freasonable steps to ensure that it
OL,14,Ffully understood both the financial
OL,15,Fand legal implications of such an
OL,16,Fadoption by undertaking the required
OL,17,Fdue diligence."
OL,19,FFairhust's safety surveys repeatedly
OL,20,Freported "no increased risk".
