OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FHowever, just nine days after an
OL,7,Finspection yielded the same
OL,8,Fconclusion, in December 2020, another
OL,9,Flandslip occurred, and some homes had
OL,10,Fto be evacuated again ` although this
OL,11,Ftime, for two nights.
OL,13,FA month later, in January 2021, there
OL,14,Fwas a third landslip, though no homes
OL,15,Fneeded to be evacuated on that
OL,16,Foccasion.
