OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FThe permanent works, when they started
OL,7,Fin March that year, cost #3m and
OL,8,Fincluded the installation of mesh
OL,9,Fnetting across the cliff face, secured
OL,10,Fby pegs, and a "catch fence barrier"
OL,11,Fat the bottom.
OL,13,FAfter this was completed, residents'
OL,14,Fgardens and fences were finally
OL,15,Freinstated along with pathways.
