OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FIn 2023, the council allocated #1.349m
OL,7,Fto its budget for the next financial
OL,8,Fyear for what was described as the
OL,9,F"final phase" of work, involving the
OL,10,Finstallation of further "protective
OL,11,Fmesh" between the slope and nearby
OL,12,Froads.
OL,14,FHowever, nearly three years later, it
OL,15,Fappears that more work remains to be
OL,16,Fdone.
