OL,3,CHow Mansfield landslide is still
OL,4,Ccausing issues six years on
OL,6,FJames Biddlestone, chief executive of
OL,7,FMansfield District Council, said:
OL,8,F"These works are a part of a planned
OL,9,Fprogramme of stabilisation works
OL,10,Fwithin the quarry, following on from
OL,11,Fthe emergency work that was completed
OL,12,Fin 2022. This next phase of the work
OL,13,Fis programmed to start towards the end
OL,14,Fof January and last for around 16
OL,15,Fweeks.
